## Architecture Reference
| Component | Primary (us-east-1) | DR (us-west-2) |
|---|---|---|
| VPC | main-vpc 10.0.0.0/16 | dr-vpc 10.1.0.0/16 |
| Load Balancer | main-alb | dr-alb (created during failover) |
| Database | main-database | Read replica promoted |
| EC2 | main-asg instances | Manually launched during failover |
